            "html": "While relatively small, the blue-ringed octopus is particularly venomous for its size.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 14"
        },
        {
            "name": "Octopus",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Octopus Species",
